author: colen
msg: OPENNLP-256 The unit test was failing because the output of string format changes according to the locale.

Added to DetailedFMeasureListener a method called createReport(Locale), where it is possible to specify the desired locale. It is overloaded by createReport(), that uses the default locale. The toString will use createReport() with the default locale.
